# The legacy `resources/mpv/` tree is kept as a dev fallback only; CI does NOT
# populate it. 7zr.exe is downloaded into resources/ during CI for Windows
# prod builds and at dev-bootstrap time (if the dev wants mpv .7z extraction
# to work without a hand-placed binary).
